OL,3,CHow 'kidult' purchases are driving
OL,4,Cgrowth in the toy industry
OL,6,FITV News' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,7,Freports on why there has been a rise
OL,8,Fin 'kidult' purchases
OL,10,FThe rise in the number of 'kidult'
OL,11,Fpurchases - adults buying toys for
OL,12,Fthemselves - is said to be behind a
OL,13,Fboom in the UK toy industry ahead of
OL,14,FChristmas.
OL,16,FNostalgia-fuelled purchases now
OL,17,Faccount for nearly a third of toy
OL,18,Fsales, figures from market research
OL,19,Fgroup Circana show.
