OL,3,CHow 'kidult' purchases are driving
OL,4,Cgrowth in the toy industry
OL,6,FThe new toy trend comes as the Toy
OL,7,FRetailers Association unveiled its
OL,8,Fpredictions for the season's top 20
OL,9,Fsellers, ranging in price from #10 to
OL,10,Falmost #80.
OL,12,FToy marketing specialist, Pamela
OL,13,FJustice, said the surge in 'kidult'
OL,14,Fpurchases may be a result of the
OL,15,F"creative element" toys can provide.
OL,17,F"You get really immersed into making
OL,18,Fit. It's the DIY, creative element,"
OL,19,Fshe told ITV News.
