OL,3,CHow 'kidult' purchases are driving
OL,4,Cgrowth in the toy industry
OL,6,F"So you have to really focus and it
OL,7,Fjust takes you away from your phone
OL,8,Fscreens, from social media."
OL,10,FAs well as having a bigger disposable
OL,11,Fincome, nostalgia is one of the
OL,12,Fdriving forces behind the surge in
OL,13,Fadults buying toys for themselves, toy
OL,14,Fimporter Richard North said.
OL,16,FFor example, he said the average age
OL,17,Fof people purchasing a cuddly Stich
OL,18,Ftoy, from Disney's Lilo and Stitch,
OL,19,Fare those in their 20's.
