OL,3,CHow 'kidult' purchases are driving
OL,4,Cgrowth in the toy industry
OL,6,F"They love brands that they remember
OL,7,Fas a kid and they've started to
OL,8,Fcollect them," he said.
OL,10,FBut it's not only a surge in 'kidult'
OL,11,Fpurchases that is helping the toy
OL,12,Findustry to boom.
OL,14,FMonthly spending on gifts for children
OL,15,Fhas increased by 35% in the past three
OL,16,Fyears - from #61 a month in 2021 to
OL,17,F#82 in 2024 - research by the Insights
OL,18,FFamily showed.
