OL,3,CHow 'kidult' purchases are driving
OL,4,Cgrowth in the toy industry
OL,6,FRosie Marshall, from the Toy Retailers
OL,7,FAssociation, said: "Toy spending has
OL,8,Factually grown this year, it has grown
OL,9,Fquite significantly, so it's
OL,10,Finteresting that parents are actually
OL,11,Fspending more money on toys for their
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,F"I think it's probably a combination
OL,15,Fof things, probably to get them away
OL,16,Ffrom digital things," she added.
